# ============================================================
# NetRecon — Target Configuration
# ============================================================
#
# Define your engagement targets here.
# Format: SITE_NAME=CIDR
#
# Example:
#   hq=192.168.1.0/24
#   branch_ny=10.10.10.0/24
#   dmz=172.16.0.0/24
#
# Rules:
#   - Site names must be lowercase, alphanumeric + underscores only
#   - One CIDR per line
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#   - Empty lines are ignored
#
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT commit this file with real target IPs.
#            The .gitignore excludes config/targets.conf
#            A template (targets.conf.example) is tracked instead.
# ============================================================

# --- Define your targets below ---
# hq=192.168.1.0/24
# datacenter=10.0.0.0/24
# branch_office=10.20.0.0/24
